Package storesystem.api.deals

Interface CartPredictate

All Superinterfaces:
java.util.function.BiPredicate<ShoppingCart,​java.lang.Boolean>, java.io.Serializable
public interface CartPredictate
extends java.io.Serializable, java.util.function.BiPredicate<ShoppingCart,​java.lang.Boolean>
Represents a serializable predicate. the first parameter is the ShoppingCart that is getting the Deal applied to them and the second is if the method should skip on any recording anything to the Deal or not. true means don't take records of the method running as it is currently peeking to see what the value will be. It is true when peekPredictate() is used.
